ğŸ§  scripts/orchestrator.py (add rolling mode)

elif args.cmd == "rolling":
    import subprocess, datetime
    subprocess.run(["python3","scripts/orchestrator.py","verify"], check=True)
    with open("verification.json") as f:
        stamp = datetime.datetime.utcnow().isoformat()+"Z"
        data = json.load(f)
        data["rolled_utc"] = stamp
    json.dump(data, open("verification.json","w"), indent=2)
    print("v153.x rolling verification complete at", stamp)

Run:

python3 scripts/orchestrator.py rolling


