ğŸ§° .github/workflows/rolling.yml

name: Rolling Verification
on:
  schedule:
    - cron: "0 */6 * * *"   # every 6 hours
jobs:
  rolling:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - run: python3 scripts/orchestrator.py rolling
      - uses: actions/upload-artifact@v4
        with:
          name: verification
          path: verification.json
      - uses: actions/configure-pages@v4
      - uses: actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3
        with:
          path: ./docs
      - uses: actions/deploy-pages@v4

This job makes v153.x a living branch: verification runs every six hours, publishing updates to GitHub Pages.


