ğŸ§¬ Behavior

1. Verification Loop â€“ automated checksum validation.


2. Self-Repair â€“ if a mismatch appears, last good build is redeployed.


3. Publication â€“ new docs auto-rendered and pushed to Pages.


4. Federation â€“ optional step exchanges lineage summaries with other mirrors.




